OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FHigh level
OL,6,Fcloud moving through this evening and
OL,7,Fovernight with the chance of some rain
OL,8,Fin the far southwest. Clearest skies
OL,9,Fin the east. Brisk winds keeping the
OL,10,Ftemperatures up overnight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FA few showers to start in
OL,13,Fthe west, otherwise hazy sunshine on
OL,14,FThursday with blustery winds. Winds
OL,15,Feasing through the day and feeling
OL,16,Fpleasant in the sunshine.
